data.description: Stunning, unique home. You are greeted with a wraparound covered porch, stonework, and double entry door. From the foyer, walk directly into the living room with an elegant stone fireplace, recessed lighting, and crisp marbled tile throughout. There is a wet bar to the left stepping into the dining area, updated lighting, and access to the back porch. Wrapped around from the front, overlooks the golf course and direct access to the back drive. Off of the dining room, a well-appointed kitchen with light granite counters and cabinets, a window looking into the courtyard, breakfast dining area. There is a glass door to the courtyard with the in-ground pool. From the foyer you can enter one wing of the house with full bathroom, secondary bedroom, also with courtyard access. The opposite hall leads to another full bathroom, secondary bedroom with direct bathroom access. Then the large, breathtaking owner's suite, with access to the wrap around porch, and large ensuite bathroom.
